<div style="border: solid 5px #999999; background:#a0bdbf; padding: 0px; margin: auto; width: 640px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>&#171; <a href="/obskuracorps-memos">Obskuracorps Memos...</a> || Black Sunrise || <a href="/a-man-of-clay-and-men-formerly-men">A Man of Clay and Men Formerly Men</a> &#187;</strong></p>
</div>
